551
00:42:55,268 --> 00:42:59,808
My brother here is not that just or loyal a person.

552
00:42:59,938 --> 00:43:03,177
He is so mean, selfish, and self-centered.

553
00:43:03,378 --> 00:43:05,177
You can take your time.

554
00:43:33,639 --> 00:43:35,309
Hello.

555
00:43:39,389 --> 00:43:40,520
Go on.

556
00:43:40,989 --> 00:43:42,819
Go in.

557
00:43:42,819 --> 00:43:44,790
(Relay Station)

558
00:44:04,679 --> 00:44:05,810
You there.

559
00:44:14,190 --> 00:44:15,659
I have not seen you before.

560
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:19,159
You over there.

561
00:44:20,860 --> 00:44:24,330
Have some mung bean pancakes. I just made them.

562
00:44:24,330 --> 00:44:25,730
- Look at the color. - Wow.

563
00:44:25,730 --> 00:44:26,730
And it smells divine.

564
00:44:26,730 --> 00:44:29,000
They taste the best when they are warm. Eat up.

565
00:44:29,239 --> 00:44:32,009
Look at that color. My gosh. You have to eat them now. Sit.

566
00:44:32,009 --> 00:44:35,310
What are you doing? Come and eat first.

567
00:44:35,310 --> 00:44:37,040
- Thank you. - Eat up.

568
00:44:37,279 --> 00:44:40,909
My gosh. Is it because we are having a feast?

569
00:44:40,980 --> 00:44:44,279
There are so many new faces. Enjoy.

570
00:44:44,279 --> 00:44:46,020
It is absolutely delicious.

571
00:44:48,190 --> 00:44:50,960
Why is this house so big? This trading group must be huge.

572
00:44:55,330 --> 00:44:57,799
The account book and medicinal herbs.

573
00:44:58,529 --> 00:44:59,730
Medicinal herbs...

574
00:45:10,940 --> 00:45:12,310
Where is the account book?

575
00:45:25,730 --> 00:45:27,690
What are you doing in here?

576
00:45:27,830 --> 00:45:31,199
You cannot be in here. You need to leave.

577
00:45:31,460 --> 00:45:33,029
I got lost while looking for the toilet.

578
00:45:35,339 --> 00:45:36,500
Oh my goodness.

579
00:45:39,940 --> 00:45:43,279
I am here. Yes. This is it. Relay station.

580
00:45:43,779 --> 00:45:44,810
I am late.

581
00:45:45,409 --> 00:45:46,750
I am late.

582
00:45:46,750 --> 00:45:49,449
Hey. I am very late.

583
00:45:49,779 --> 00:45:53,489
- Wait. Hold on. I am coming. - Oh no.

584
00:45:53,489 --> 00:45:56,659
- Oh no. I remember now. - Coming. Wait.

585
00:46:00,630 --> 00:46:02,029
I have brought a letter.

586
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:05,130
What? Get lost.

587
00:46:07,029 --> 00:46:09,339
(Relay Station)

588
00:46:16,810 --> 00:46:18,980
Please keep it down.

589
00:46:23,679 --> 00:46:25,850
Help me.

590
00:46:29,759 --> 00:46:30,889
My gosh.

591
00:46:40,500 --> 00:46:41,600
Are you all right?

592
00:46:42,239 --> 00:46:43,299
Master.

593
00:46:46,369 --> 00:46:47,770
What happened?

594
00:46:48,610 --> 00:46:51,179
Master. Why did you come here?

595
00:46:52,549 --> 00:46:55,679
I was searching the house and heard you scream.

596
00:46:57,179 --> 00:46:58,319
That is what led me here.

597
00:47:00,350 --> 00:47:01,819
There is no time for this.

598
00:47:02,119 --> 00:47:05,190
If you are seen anywhere around here...

599
00:47:11,730 --> 00:47:13,100
You are dead.

600
00:47:45,429 --> 00:47:46,630
Gosh.

601
00:47:56,110 --> 00:47:58,110
Oh no. What now?

602
00:48:08,989 --> 00:48:10,119
What did I say?

603
00:48:10,460 --> 00:48:12,130
As I said, if he does not return in 15 minutes,

604
00:48:13,759 --> 00:48:15,060
he is a rat.

605
00:48:15,299 --> 00:48:18,100
Honest truth, you had my heart,

606
00:48:18,529 --> 00:48:19,869
Pal Soon.

607
00:48:20,469 --> 00:48:22,369
Tell me what is going on.

608
00:48:23,199 --> 00:48:24,639
Explain yourself.

609
00:48:26,540 --> 00:48:27,710
Sorry about that.

610
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:30,480
This is a misunderstanding.

611
00:48:30,480 --> 00:48:33,880
We did not go into your shed to steal. He got lost...

612
00:48:33,880 --> 00:48:35,779
- and stepped on a trap... - He got lost,

613
00:48:35,850 --> 00:48:37,679
but he went into someone else's storage shed.

614
00:48:38,819 --> 00:48:43,020
It was all because I was careless.

615
00:48:43,159 --> 00:48:46,089
Your shed was so grand and beautiful,

616
00:48:46,190 --> 00:48:50,259
that I wanted to take a look. I apologize.

617
00:48:50,429 --> 00:48:51,630
Sorry about that.

618
00:48:52,770 --> 00:48:55,339
How dare you continue to act like you are a nobleman?

619
00:49:01,569 --> 00:49:03,040
Are you really with the saheonbu?

620
00:49:13,119 --> 00:49:15,889
Hey. Drag them away...

621
00:49:16,319 --> 00:49:17,460
and search them.

622
00:49:17,690 --> 00:49:18,790
- Yes, my lord. - Yes, my lord.

623
00:49:19,230 --> 00:49:22,560
(Ra Yi Eon)

624
00:49:22,560 --> 00:49:23,659
Letter.

625
00:49:26,130 --> 00:49:28,569
Wake up! Everyone wake up!

626
00:49:28,699 --> 00:49:30,199
- Why you... - Master.

627
00:49:30,199 --> 00:49:31,540
He is my husband.

628
00:50:00,929 --> 00:50:04,299
You are driving me mad. I cannot stand it.

629
00:50:04,600 --> 00:50:07,170
You keep failing the state exam but have not learned your lesson.

630
00:50:07,310 --> 00:50:09,440
You said you would live in a temple and study,

631
00:50:09,440 --> 00:50:12,279
but you are visiting banquets and drinking again?

632
00:50:15,449 --> 00:50:17,949
When will you grow up?

633
00:50:17,949 --> 00:50:21,489
You have inherited so much from Father including farms and fields.

634
00:50:21,489 --> 00:50:23,520
How long will you live like this?

635
00:50:23,889 --> 00:50:26,690
- I just cannot stand it. - Wait.

636
00:50:26,929 --> 00:50:28,259
Wait.

637
00:50:30,799 --> 00:50:33,699
I was wrong. I am sorry.

638
00:50:35,600 --> 00:50:37,239
I am going to kill you.

639
00:50:37,239 --> 00:50:39,310
- Die. - Wait.

640
00:50:43,639 --> 00:50:44,839
What is that?

641
00:50:48,350 --> 00:50:52,150
(Relay Station)

642
00:50:52,790 --> 00:50:54,350
Enough!

643
00:51:04,860 --> 00:51:07,670
Are you really this man's wife?

644
00:51:10,770 --> 00:51:11,909
Yes, I am.

645
00:51:11,909 --> 00:51:13,739
I wish I were not.

646
00:51:13,909 --> 00:51:18,110
You do not know how much it kills me to have a husband like him.

647
00:51:20,949 --> 00:51:22,319
Actually,

648
00:51:22,580 --> 00:51:24,949
it may be better for me...

649
00:51:24,949 --> 00:51:27,549
if you just kill him right now.

650
00:51:27,750 --> 00:51:30,159
I am so sick of him.

651
00:51:30,219 --> 00:51:32,130
I wish he were gone.

652
00:51:37,130 --> 00:51:38,360
What are you doing?

653
00:51:38,730 --> 00:51:39,799
Sit.

654
00:51:42,199 --> 00:51:44,239
If you two really are husband and wife,

655
00:51:45,670 --> 00:51:46,869
kiss.

656
00:51:48,339 --> 00:51:49,409
Pardon?

657
00:51:53,980 --> 00:51:55,679
Either kiss...

658
00:51:56,119 --> 00:51:59,889
or shout, "The king is a donkey's behind!"

659
00:51:59,889 --> 00:52:01,190
Your choice.

660
00:52:01,350 --> 00:52:02,420
Pardon?

661
00:52:12,130 --> 00:52:13,330
Do it.

662
00:52:17,969 --> 00:52:19,210
What do you say?

663
00:52:19,210 --> 00:52:20,940
Why is he hesitating?

664
00:52:22,080 --> 00:52:24,639
It would be his first kiss.

665
00:52:27,949 --> 00:52:30,650
Would it not be better to say the king is... You know?

666
00:52:36,460 --> 00:52:37,560
The king...

667
00:52:43,299 --> 00:52:45,500
The king is a donkey's...

668
00:53:04,819 --> 00:53:07,650
Even if you have no desire to succeed,

669
00:53:08,049 --> 00:53:10,989
how could you insult the king?

670
00:53:11,259 --> 00:53:13,389
In front of all these people.

671
00:53:13,389 --> 00:53:14,659
What if someone reports you?

672
00:53:15,659 --> 00:53:19,100
You will be arrested for contempt and face the gravest punishment!

673
00:53:20,199 --> 00:53:23,040
The soldiers will be here soon. Hang in there.

674
00:53:25,739 --> 00:53:27,310
And you are making a mistake too.

675
00:53:27,569 --> 00:53:29,810
I understand that my husband wronged you first.

676
00:53:29,880 --> 00:53:32,650
But how could you be so reckless?

677
00:53:32,980 --> 00:53:36,080
I am sure you know that we must not even joke...

678
00:53:36,850 --> 00:53:38,080
about the King.

679
00:53:44,860 --> 00:53:46,529
You know no shame, woman.

680
00:53:47,730 --> 00:53:49,630
You have no problem kissing a man in front of others.

681
00:53:50,500 --> 00:53:51,799
Are you always that promiscuous?

682
00:53:58,600 --> 00:54:00,069
No, I am not.

683
00:54:02,909 --> 00:54:04,040
But...

684
00:54:04,239 --> 00:54:05,909
So what if I am?

685
00:54:09,679 --> 00:54:10,750
I see.

686
00:54:13,389 --> 00:54:14,520
Then how about this?

687
00:54:15,819 --> 00:54:17,219
If you kiss me,

688
00:54:18,659 --> 00:54:20,330
I will release everyone here.

689
00:54:20,860 --> 00:54:21,989
Watch your tongue!

690
00:54:26,100 --> 00:54:28,130
I do not care what you think about the King.

691
00:54:28,839 --> 00:54:30,400
But do not insult my wife.

692
00:54:40,409 --> 00:54:42,619
You guys cannot be married.

693
00:54:44,219 --> 00:54:46,589
