698
00:55:03,500 --> 00:55:04,739
Who are you?

699
00:55:05,770 --> 00:55:06,770
Answer me.

700
00:55:08,940 --> 00:55:10,580
Who on earth are you?

701
00:55:19,889 --> 00:55:21,949
Allow us to share a kiss.

702
00:55:23,219 --> 00:55:24,920
Or let her die on my sword.

703
00:55:26,330 --> 00:55:29,699
If you can make a decision, I will let the rest of you live.

704
00:55:34,029 --> 00:55:36,069
- Let us go! - Go!

705
00:55:39,909 --> 00:55:41,170
